  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "TILER",
  "description": "<h1>Job Description & Requirements</h1><p>We are looking for a skilled and reliable <strong>Tiler</strong> to join our construction and renovation team. The successful candidate will be responsible for installing and finishing tiles on floors and other surfaces for residential and commercial projects across Singapore.</p><h2>Roles & Responsibilities</h2><ul><li><p>Prepare surfaces by cleaning, leveling, and applying adhesive or mortar</p></li><li><p>Measure, cut, and lay tiles accurately (ceramic, porcelain, marble, granite, and mosaic)</p></li><li><p>Ensure tiles are aligned, level, and evenly spaced</p></li><li><p>Apply grout and seal joints for a clean and durable finish</p></li><li><p>Repair and replace damaged or broken tiles</p></li><li><p>Read basic drawings and follow work instructions from supervisors</p></li><li><p>Maintain tools and keep work areas clean and safe</p></li><li><p>Follow workplace safety and company procedures</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with team members to meet project timelines</p></li></ul><h2>Requirements</h2><ul><li><p>Minimum <strong>2 years of relevant experience</strong> in tiling works</p></li><li><p>Experience with floor and wall tiling in residential and commercial projects</p></li><li><p>Ability to use tiling tools and cutting machines safely</p></li><li><p>Physically fit and able to work on site</p></li><li><p>Knowledge of workplace safety practices</p></li><li><p>Willing to work overtime, weekends, and at different job locations when required</p></li><li><p>Team player with a responsible and positive work attitude</p></li></ul>",
